OneMeanDream 0.1.2
  • Reference
    • Getting Started
  • News
Performs one-sample t-tests using Wallace critical value approximation and Hastings p-value approximation. Includes comprehensive assumption checks (normality via Shapiro-Wilk, outlier detection) and diagnostic plots.
